			DORAND 5
				SAY I am a simple Paladin.
				SAY I uphold Honor!
				SAY I am a Paladin, <SRC.SEX good sir/good milady>.
				SAY I am a Paladin, <SRC.SEX Mi'lord/Mi'lady>.
				SAY I represent Honor to the populace of Britannia, <SRC.SEX good sir/good lady>
			ENDDO
		ELSE
			DORAND 5
				SAY I am a simple Paladin.
				SAY I uphold Honor!
				SAY I am a Paladin, <SRC.SEX good sir/good milady>.
				SAY I am a Paladin, <SRC.SEX Mi'lord/Mi'lady>.
				SAY I represent Honor to the populace of Britannia, <SRC.SEX good sir/good lady>
			ENDDO
		ENDIF
	ENDIF

